{
  "text": "In this section we recall the main results of [CITATION_1] concerning the squeezing in presence of particle losses, and we use these results to show an analogy between the effect of the losses and the effect of the dephasing Hamiltonian (15) in the thermodynamic limit.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "11167696"
